'''檸檬酸銫'''是一種[[有機化合物|有機化合物]]，為一種[[銫|銫]]的[[檸檬酸鹽|檸檬酸鹽]]，其化學式為Cs<sub>3</sub>C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>5</sub>O<sub>7</sub>。它是可溶于水的白色固体。<ref>{{cite book | last=Schweitzer | first=G.K. | last2=Pesterfield | first2=L.L. | title=The Aqueous Chemistry of the Elements | publisher=Oxford University Press | year=2010 | isbn=978-0-19-974219-6 | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-TNhhlGcCzwC&pg=PA120 | access-date=2021-10-29 | page=120 | archive-date=2021-10-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211029071721/https://books.google.com/books?id=-TNhhlGcCzwC&pg=PA120 | dead-url=no }}</ref>它可用于<sup>227</sup>Ac和<sup>226</sup>Ra电解分离过程中的添加物。<ref>Boue-Ruelle, F.; Bouissieres, G.; David, F.; Legoux, Y.; Muxart, R.; Rogelet, P.; Zuppiroli, G. Separation of actinium-​227 formed by neutron irradiation of radium-​226. ''Revue de Chimie Minerale'', 1974. 11 (4): 466-473.</ref>

== 制備 ==
檸檬酸銫可由[[檸檬酸|檸檬酸]]和[[氢氧化銫|氢氧化銫]]的[[酸鹼中和|酸鹼中和]]反应製得。<ref>{{cite journal|journal=Inorganic Chemistry|volume=58|issue=2|language=en|issn=0020-1669|date=2019-01-22|pages=1012–1015|doi=10.1021/acs.inorgchem.8b03139|url=https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.inorgchem.8b03139|title=Hexaniobate Cluster Anion Monolayers on Gold Nanoparticles: A New Structural Role for Alkali Metal Countercations|accessdate=2021-10-29|author=Shelly Sharet Leiser, Libi Polin, Gal Gan-Or, Manoj Raula, Ira A. Weinstock|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109022859/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/10.1021/acs.inorgchem.8b03139|dead-url=no}}</ref>
: <chem>3 CsOH + C6H8O7 -> Cs3C6H5O7 + 3 H2O</chem>

